  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "Further processing of this dataset was carried out by eliminating products that occur as reactants in the same reaction, the removal of known co-enzymes, common by-products, the reaction with more than one product or no reactants (missing data) and so on [21].",
    "Following this, for further preprocessing, the ECREACT dataset was first separated into two parts: the 'substrate-product' reaction parts in SMILES (Simplified Molecular Input Line Entry System) format and the EC number tags.",
    "We then refined the dataset by removing reactions that only had EC-level 1 classification.",
    "To better organize the data, we labeled the EC numbers associated with the reaction SMILES from EC-level 3, resulting in a total of 308 labels.",
    "The final dataset contains 56,512 enzymatic reactions with 308 EC sub-subclass labels."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "Further processing of this dataset was carried out by eliminating products that occur as reactants in the same reaction, the removal of known co-enzymes, common by-products, the reaction with more than one product or no reactants (missing data) and so on [21]."
  ]
